# Per-project bundled data lives here.
#
# This directory is for small CSVs (or similar) that ship WITH the algorithm —
# uploaded by `lean cloud push`, read in Initialize from disk. No runtime HTTP
# calls from the algorithm itself.
#
# Distinct from MyProjects/data/ at the workspace level, which is gitignored
# and used for regenerable local fixtures. THIS directory's CSV files ARE
# committable. See workspace AGENTS.md § "Bundled Per-Project Data".
#
# Pair with `tools/refresh_<name>.py` for a one-off fetcher.
